descriptionHtml:
Triplette Nords. These girls may look alike, yet they are very different in nature. They are deadly, but wont die, marriagable and will level with you. 
These girls are staying at the Temple of Kynareth in Whiterun, you have to look around.
Just pick them up, dress them and have fun, No need to change anything but if you wish to change them, do so yourself.

They are all wearing basic hunting gear when you get them, so you can dress them as you please. The pictures are what i dress them in.

IMPORTANT or the game will crash

WARNING
You must have ApachiiHair running for this mod. Make sure it is before Kammie n the order.
